text: Hi Darci! Somehow I didn't get the notification that you messaged! So sorry it has taken me so long to respond to you!

I graduated with a 2:1 in BA Animation Production from the Arts University Bournemouth. The only title on my production experience, as of current, is my graduate film "Sweetness and Light" where I was producer, and Head of CG (across all aspects of the pipeline). I'm London based currently. I want to work as a producer for VFX as my long term goal. So I've been applying to a lot of production assistant and runner positions at the moment. However, I'm not opposed to other forms of producing, I think there is a lot to learn from every area.

You're dog sounds absolutely adorable! I used to have a golden retriever dogs are honestly the most fun animals (don't tell my cat) :sweat_smile: I want to travel the world some day, but at the moment I've mostly seen a lot of Europe as its pretty easy and cheap!!
I had an interview for a runner position at The Mill on Nov 6th. I think they were all full up on production runners tho, so next time!
Hopefully I get a notification next time, so I can be faster with my response! Speak soon
